videos.description: Northwestern quarterback Clayton Thorson is sacked on third down by Cavon Walker for a loss of 4 yards forcing the Wildcats to punt.
videos.headline: Maryland defense registers drive-ending sack

videos.description: Max Bortenschlager drops back and finds D.J. Moore in the slot for the 12-yard touchdown pass to put the Terrapins in the lead.
videos.headline: Maryland scores on 12-yard catch from Moore

videos.description: Clayton Thorson throws to the left side and his pass is intercepted by Darnell Savage Jr. to give the ball back to Maryland.
videos.headline: Savage makes nice catch for interception

videos.description: Justin Jackson finds a hole and runs it up the middle for a 5-yard touchdown giving the Wildcats the lead.
videos.headline: Jackson's short TD run puts Northwestern ahead

videos.description: Clayton Thorson keeps the ball and runs for an 18-yard touchdown to put the Wildcats back in the lead.
videos.headline: Thorson  uses legs to score for Northwestern

videos.description: Clayton Thorson connects with Flynn Nagel who dives in to the end zone extending the Wildcats' lead going into the half.
videos.headline: Northwestern scores TD right before halftime

videos.description: Northwestern head coach Pat Fitzgerald says Clayton Thorson has been playing at a high level because his offensive line is giving him time to create plays.
videos.headline: Fitzgerald credits the o-line for success on offense

videos.description: Max Bortenschlager throws a perfect 20-yard pass to Taivon Jacobs for a touchdown to cut Northwestern's lead.
videos.headline: Bortenschlager throws laser TD pass

videos.description: Clayton Thorson throws to the end zone but his pass is intercepted by JC Jackson giving Maryland the ball back as they trail by one score.
videos.headline: Maryland defense gets timely interception

videos.description: After a tackle QB Max Bortenschlager leaves the game with an injury putting Maryland on their final scholarship quarterback. After being checked out he returned to the game.
videos.headline: Bortenschlager temporarily leaves game with injury

videos.description: Justin Jackson breaks for a 21-yard touchdown run to add to Northwestern's lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Jackson gets 2nd TD of the day
